cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DL

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with sentiment analysis and natural language processing. It may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel method for sentiment analysis. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of machine learning techniques. It may also fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as sentiment analysis is often used in information retrieval tasks. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.DL (Deep Learning) as deep learning techniques are used in the proposed method.
